data.value: Get your trip off to a great start with a stay at this property, which offers free Wi-Fi in all rooms. Conveniently situated in the Mandaue City part of Cebu this property puts you close to attractions and interesting dining options.

data.value: Conveniently situated in the Cebu City part of Cebu, this property puts you close to attractions and interesting dining options. Don't leave before paying a visit to the famous Basilica De Sto. Nino.
